name: Welcome to Web3: Token 002
description:
How do you DYOR (or Do Your Own Research) in web3? Well, start with the resources here as a guide to best practice. Just click on the links in the image to go straight to the sources. And you were thinking that NFTs were just .JPEGs...

Welcome to Web3 is a project to help newcomers better understand and engage in Web3/NFTs/Crypto.
